5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","The Gap"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in The Gap? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across The Gap, Ashgrove, Keperra and Bardon. Our 5-star instructors help The Gap students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Geographically isolated and surrounded by heavy forest, The Gap features highly expansive, sprawling residential networks converging onto a single, heavily trafficked spine: Waterworks Road. The environment is extremely hilly, meaning learners are immediately tested on their braking discipline and gradient control."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Because the suburb’s internal streets operate as a vast cul-de-sac system, our instructors can train absolute beginners in complete isolation from through-traffic. As their skills mature, getting out of the suburb requires mastering the high-speed, multi-lane merge onto Waterworks Road, perfectly simulating the pressure required for their Toowong practical test."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"The Gap learners sit their test at the Toowong TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from The Gap, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-gray-900 block mb-1","children":"Wat